##### Importing Modules in Python: Modules and Packages
- In Python, modules and packages help organize and reuse code. Here's a comprehensive guide on how to import them.
import math
math.sqrt(16)
from math import sqrt,pi
print(sqrt(16))
print(sqrt(25))
print(pi)
import numpy as np
np.array([1,2,3,4])
from math import *
print(sqrt(16))
print(pi)
